short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds three buttons to examappointments.com (TAB) used to generate custom reports for tracking patient copays.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a third party application that hooks into Luxottica's TAB and adds three simple reports for tracking patient copays. These can be found under the "Reports" page in TAB.
